WHO   — Vincent's Camera — Sonya's Lazarus as a lens
WHAT  — The one inspired piece of adaptation: where Sonya reads Lazarus, Vincent photographs — redemption as the act of being truly seen.
WHERE — CPS · Crime + Punishment in Suburbia  Framework inputs: Crime + Punishment in Suburbia (2000)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
